about: Hi! My name is Bolu Akindele and I am a junior at Murray State University. I am interning at Tyler Technologies working on the Time and Attendance team. I have backend experience with C#, Java, and Python, and frontend experience in Javascript and React.js. I also have database experience with Microsoft SQL. I am apart of my university's Association of Computer Machinery club and Black Student Council, where I serve as the Vice President.
